headline: PDD Holdings Stock Sees Composite Rating Climb To 97
summary: PDD Holdings stock saw its IBD SmartSelect Composite Rating rise to 97 Friday, up from 94 the day before.  PDD Holdings stock recently reclaimed its 200-day moving average and is not currently near a proper buy zone.  The stock has a 99 EPS Rating, which means its recent quarterly and annual earnings growth is outpacing 99% of all stocks.
